01:16:54,701 --> 01:16:56,821
I have been high quite
often on cannabis.

1239
01:16:56,981 --> 01:16:58,741
But I have never managed
to reach Canada.

1240
01:16:59,541 --> 01:17:01,381
It's not Canada, it's death.

1241
01:17:02,021 --> 01:17:04,621
Life is short,
follow the right path.

1242
01:17:04,821 --> 01:17:06,301
Follow the right path.

1243
01:17:07,261 --> 01:17:09,181
Who wants words of wisdom
from the wise?

1244
01:17:09,621 --> 01:17:12,461
The drugs you are taking will one
day make you sell your car.

1245
01:17:28,141 --> 01:17:29,581
What's wrong, grandma?

1246
01:17:30,981 --> 01:17:32,861
My sister's granddaughter
is getting married.

1247
01:17:33,701 --> 01:17:34,981
You want to attend it?

1248
01:17:35,221 --> 01:17:36,621
What will I do there?

1249
01:17:38,141 --> 01:17:41,341
That means you want to go there.

1250
01:17:42,421 --> 01:17:43,461
Kash..

1251
01:17:43,701 --> 01:17:45,421
Shall we? -What will I do there?

1252
01:17:47,861 --> 01:17:48,861
Ouch!

1253
01:17:49,701 --> 01:17:50,861
God!

1254
01:17:51,941 --> 01:17:53,421
Grandma.. -Let me sleep.

1255
01:18:01,621 --> 01:18:02,621
Hello?

1256
01:18:02,701 --> 01:18:04,901
Where are you, knucklehead?

1257
01:18:05,061 --> 01:18:06,981
Don't curse, uncle.

1258
01:18:07,101 --> 01:18:08,861
Grandma, want some?
-I say what you are..

1259
01:18:08,941 --> 01:18:10,341
..I can't that now, can I?

1260
01:18:10,461 --> 01:18:13,901
Scoundrel, I am worried about
you. Where are you?

1261
01:18:13,981 --> 01:18:16,421
Uncle,
our vehicle is on the road.

1262
01:18:16,821 --> 01:18:19,261
I am making money here.
Don't worry.

1263
01:18:19,381 --> 01:18:22,421
I worry because you don't
have a permit.

1264
01:18:24,421 --> 01:18:25,621
Speak up now, will you?

1265
01:18:25,941 --> 01:18:26,941
Hello?

1266
01:18:27,581 --> 01:18:28,821
I'll tall you to later.

1267
01:18:29,461 --> 01:18:30,821
He disconnected it, again.

1268
01:18:31,581 --> 01:18:32,581
Give me a biscuit.

1269
01:18:35,061 --> 01:18:36,621
There is a police
check post ahead.

1270
01:18:36,981 --> 01:18:38,261
And I don't have a permit.

1271
01:18:38,421 --> 01:18:40,701
If they ask, tell them this
is your family car. -Okay.

1272
01:18:44,301 --> 01:18:46,141
License and registration, please.

1273
01:18:46,221 --> 01:18:48,101
Show us all the documents.
-Go on.

1274
01:18:48,861 --> 01:18:50,301
I have all the documents.

1275
01:18:50,621 --> 01:18:51,861
Here's my license.

1276
01:18:54,101 --> 01:18:55,381
And here's the insurance.

1277
01:18:56,221 --> 01:18:58,301
I have a pollution under
control certificate too.

1278
01:19:02,461 --> 01:19:05,061
Who are they, your passengers?
-No, my family.

1279
01:19:05,581 --> 01:19:08,061
He is my grandson and
they are his sisters.

1280
01:19:08,301 --> 01:19:09,661
We're going for a wedding.

1281
01:19:10,341 --> 01:19:13,301
Reshma, let them pass. -What?

1282
01:19:26,861 --> 01:19:27,981
Oh God!

1283
01:19:32,021 --> 01:19:33,021
Sisters?

1284
01:19:33,581 --> 01:19:34,981
What's wrong with him, girls?

1285
01:19:39,701 --> 01:19:41,301
