They aren't my sisters.

1287
01:19:44,261 --> 01:19:45,261
Then who are they?

1288
01:19:46,181 --> 01:19:48,141
One is my wife and the
other is her sister.

1289
01:19:48,381 --> 01:19:49,981
Then too they are your family.

1290
01:19:50,941 --> 01:19:52,941
Yes.
-It's okay, give me a ticket.

1291
01:19:53,781 --> 01:19:55,661
Shinda, give him a ticket.

1292
01:19:55,941 --> 01:19:57,381
Where did that pigeon go?

1293
01:19:57,621 --> 01:19:59,061
I don't know what is he up to.

1294
01:20:08,021 --> 01:20:09,341
I think he is crazy.

1295
01:20:09,661 --> 01:20:10,661
Thank you.

1296
01:20:19,461 --> 01:20:20,821
Here's the ticket.

1297
01:20:20,901 --> 01:20:22,821
'There are other relationships
in the world..'

1298
01:20:22,901 --> 01:20:24,301
'..than that of a brother
and sister.'

1299
01:20:24,381 --> 01:20:26,301
'The girls are ready
to get married..'

1300
01:20:26,941 --> 01:20:29,181
