Oh damn!

1305
01:21:15,541 --> 01:21:16,541
Sister is here!

1306
01:21:22,821 --> 01:21:24,141
I seek your blessings.

1307
01:21:24,341 --> 01:21:25,701
Hello, sister.

1308
01:21:25,781 --> 01:21:27,581
God bless you, brother.

1309
01:21:27,941 --> 01:21:30,541
My sister, the cop is here.

1310
01:21:30,661 --> 01:21:31,661
I am so happy!

1311
01:21:31,781 --> 01:21:33,941
Hello, mother.

1312
01:21:33,981 --> 01:21:35,781
