shameless ones!

1313
01:21:35,861 --> 01:21:38,461
We are here since yesterday.
-These fritters are delicious.

1314
01:21:38,581 --> 01:21:39,981
Let's eat them. -Amazing.

1315
01:21:40,621 --> 01:21:44,821
Black hair,
glowing face, dark glasses..

1316
01:21:44,901 --> 01:21:47,261
Our sister is getting
younger by the day.

1317
01:21:47,341 --> 01:21:49,021
I hope she doesn't cause
much trouble.

1318
01:21:49,101 --> 01:21:50,741
I'll have to give dowry again.

1319
01:21:50,821 --> 01:21:53,261
Dowry? Like you gave me the
Taj Mahal as dowry earlier.

1320
01:21:53,581 --> 01:21:55,821
These girls are behind
this change.

1321
01:21:55,901 --> 01:21:57,821
Say hello, girls. -Hello.

1322
01:21:57,901 --> 01:21:59,381
He is my brother, Janta.
-God bless you.

1323
01:21:59,461 --> 01:22:00,861
And she is my sister, Golo.

1324
01:22:01,141 --> 01:22:03,901
Sister, these girls?
-Manjeeti's daughters.

1325
01:22:04,021 --> 01:22:05,461
Oh wonderful!

1326
01:22:05,581 --> 01:22:07,221
These girls are all grown up!

1327
01:22:07,421 --> 01:22:09,421
I seek your blessings, aunt.
-God bless you, son.

1328
01:22:09,541 --> 01:22:11,901
We feel blessed with
your presence.

1329
01:22:11,981 --> 01:22:13,701
This wedding celebration
just became more alive.

1330
01:22:13,781 --> 01:22:15,861
Mother won't just stop talking.

1331
01:22:15,981 --> 01:22:18,101
How about letting aunt have
some water at least.

1332
01:22:18,181 --> 01:22:20,141
Let's go, aunt. -Let's go, son.

1333
01:22:20,981 --> 01:22:23,381
Boys, serve tea.

1334
