becomes a famous singer.

1460
01:30:03,101 --> 01:30:06,821
Really? -Do you remember you had
once brought me a harmonium?

1461
01:30:06,901 --> 01:30:07,941
Yes, I do.

1462
01:30:08,101 --> 01:30:10,381
