sister's support.

1467
01:30:24,181 --> 01:30:25,341
You are right, sister.

1468
01:30:26,141 --> 01:30:28,661
She isn't our elder sister,
she is our mother.

1469
01:30:30,581 --> 01:30:35,901
I too wanted a guitar,
but never brought me one.

1470
01:30:55,381 --> 01:30:56,461
Careful there.

1471
